author: Ted Byrne
content:
Hmmmm..... another tunnel. This one also reddish lined but even shinier. I like this, liked #536 even more. Great set and in fact I wonder if maybe I'm the guy who needs an appointment with a Viennese shrink?

Seriously, you and Craig Tanner just now are really investigating the ancient and powerful mystery of the tunnel.. and you are doing it with clout.
